001package com.technototes.path.subsystem;
002
003import java.lang.annotation.Annotation;
004import java.lang.annotation.ElementType;
005import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
006import java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;
007import java.lang.annotation.Target;
008import java.lang.reflect.Field;
009
010@SuppressWarnings("unused")
011@FunctionalInterface
012public interface DeadWheelConstants {
013
014    Class getConstant();
015
016    default double getDouble(Class<? extends Annotation> a) {
017        for (Field f : getConstant().getFields()) {
018            try {
019                if (f.isAnnotationPresent(a)) {
020                    System.out.println(a.toString() + " as " + f.getDouble(null));
021                    return f.getDouble(null);
022                }
023            } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {
024                System.err.println(f.getType() + " is inaccessible for some reason");
025            }
026        }
027        return 0;
028    }
029
030    default boolean getBoolean(Class<? extends Annotation> a) {
031        for (Field f : getConstant().getFields()) {
032            try {
033                if (f.isAnnotationPresent(a)) {
034                    System.out.println(a.toString() + " as " + f.getBoolean(null));
035                    return f.getBoolean(null);
036                }
037            } catch (IllegalAccessException e) {
038                System.err.println(f.getType() + " is inaccessible for some reason");
039            }
040        }
041        return false;
042    }
043
044    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
045    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
046    @interface LateralDistance {}
047
048    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
049    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
050    @interface ForwardOffset {}
051
052    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
053    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
054    @interface EncoderOverflow {}
055
056    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
057    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
058    @interface GearRatio {}
059
060    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
061    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
062    @interface TicksPerRev {}
063
064    @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
065    @Target(ElementType.FIELD)
066    @interface WheelRadius {}
067
068    static double encoderTicksToInches(double ticks, double rad, double rat, double rev) {
069        return rad * 2 * Math.PI * rat * ticks / rev;
070    }
071
072    static double rpmToVelocity(double rpm, double rad, double rat) {
073        return rpm * rat * 2 * Math.PI * rad / 60.0;
074    }
075
076    static double getMotorVelocityF(double ticksPerSecond) {
077        return 32767 / ticksPerSecond;
078    }
079}
